{"tid":159783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近成日發惡夢 有無方法唔好再係咁","createTime":"2017-03-17T08:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T13:39:18.000Z","uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de8e14e5a206778008ab721247895bd433376067","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"連續幾晚都發惡夢<br />\n惡夢都離唔開男朋友<br />\n第一晚就發夢見到自己同唔識但年紀大好多既男人結婚<br />\n但結果陣係咁諗起男朋友跟住係咁喊<br />\n第二晚就係見到男朋友去左大陸讀書識左個大波長腿妹<br />\n跟住唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚就係生日去旅行果日掉低我由我自己去旅行<br />\n但佢去左韓國自己玩<br />\n<br />\n到底我發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e397eb36e83a945cbfc78beb954e643357f9b3","tid":159783,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"唔好訓"},{"pid":"c2b6ee2207602f81e369035fc02fd2a39d94d902","tid":159783,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"煩膠"},{"pid":"479f0b677db06c2df9a293d2f2b09be3ef77dcb3","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我已經日日都5點幾先訓..."},{"pid":"c07cd3ec82ac612ff4a7489dda5984c530924f26","tid":159783,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"同我扑返獲，再發男友對唔住你既夢會平衡番，好訓D"},{"pid":"d16330e2e69a2cb6792a84b5bcd5d67f45e05498","tid":159783,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:05:14.000Z","msg":"你條仔<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span>你"},{"pid":"568ac6ae5815a7915081428dab2b934258d25019","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我扑返獲，再發男友對唔住你既夢會平衡番，好訓D</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk