32f5c87","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攬住羊仔訓</blockquote><br />\n羊仔我之前個男朋友送架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4024192993c6ce050308caee2e8731bf94770a","tid":159783,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>攬住羊仔訓</blockquote><br />\n羊仔我之前個男朋友送架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔攬得咩"},{"pid":"19d085afa2e475ae5eda591822faf6bc89ce0c6a","tid":159783,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"我係發鬼夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇撚到唔敢訓"},{"pid":"122a4a966af90d91baf2384c002418c3be9820a8","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係發鬼夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇撚到唔敢訓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩夢黎講黎聽下"},{"pid":"175f63edd91cb55ae8b5246089b0ecf9875eae69","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>攬住羊仔訓</blockquote><br />\n羊仔我之前個男朋友送架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔攬得咩</blockquote><br />\n我有熊仔 我細個果陣屋企人買比我我仲攬住佢訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37286e77dfce76df3bc1341576dec3903d1f91a2","tid":159783,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:33:51.000Z","msg":"dump左隻熊仔啦 買amuse既羊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d060759734f1a82760ad31886758ee9219f1bc5","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dump左隻熊仔啦 買amuse既羊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔忍心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好鐘意隻熊仔 雖然佢個樣好殘"},{"pid":"619efff904e00c6dfeba74ecabf210d7971baa20","tid":159783,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係發鬼夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇撚到唔敢訓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩夢黎講黎聽下</blockquote><br />\n好長喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35519b523b65dd67f215b658e87f3b3a10d9f409","tid":159783,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係發鬼夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇撚到唔敢訓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩夢黎講黎聽下</blockquote><br />\n好長喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b08bb118a9ebe1b8942b4efe405088da56a5c9","tid":159783,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係發鬼夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇撚到唔敢訓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩夢黎講黎聽下</blockquote><br />\n好長喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n照打先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解我住我本身個到既樓上 本身住20樓 所有行李都係21樓啦 <br />\n返屋企要拍卡 我又冇帶 就同個看更嘈話我住20 佢地話20樓冇我呢個人 我就話我屋企人住20我自己21 21樓拎黎擺行李 吉既間屋 <br />\n之後就等lift 原來我家姐企我前面聽到我同看更講野 之後佢個身唔郁 頸擰轉話水黎對住我笑左下 勁撚寒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後個畫面變左我係21樓吉個間屋 我訓緊教 見到我斜對面 我張床格離有個黑色既人 好似燒死左既細路 男仔黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我就大叫 先醒起佢地係樓下得我自己係樓上 心諗仆街冇人救我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌真係完全郁唔撚到 個鬼細路係撚咁望住我 好驚好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係以為我會醒唔返 永遠係個夢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999, 諗返起仲係好驚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}